name: Nightmares Made Flesh 01
description:
My body, what's left of it, is paralyzed with fear. What is this thing? Why is it gorging on my torn and mangled flesh? The pain is unbearable, I just want to die already. This agony is too much...

This has to be a dream. It has to be. I remember laying down and playing on my phone for an hour. This is a dream. Why can't I wake up?
